It’s an old ImageClub typeface called Too Much Opaque, but it doesn’t seem to be commercially available anymore.

There is a freemium version, however, called OverMuch:  
 [http://www.dafont.com/overmuch.font?text=DOUBLE](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317203413/http:/www.dafont.com/overmuch.font?text=DOUBLE "http://www.dafont.com/overmuch.font?text=DOUBLE")
